data.description: Come see this well kept charmer. This home has an open floor plan, gas stove with center island. It's close to the toll road, shopping, restaurants and the ACC Campus. This community has a pool, playground, picnic area and a community center. Fun times to had in Elgin with public parks, farmer's markets and much more. The contract for this home will require court approval. ALL OFFERS WILL BE GIVEN SERIOUS CONSIDERATION.
